$CMP MAU102
D The  MAU100 series is a range of 1W DC-DC converters in a small SIP Package featuring I/O isolation of 1000VDC. An excellent efficiency allows an operating temperature range of 40 to +85. These converters offer an economical solution for many applications where a voltage has to be isolated.
